data.title: Time Magazine Archive
data.meta_description: With a focus on news, and with coverage of a wide array of subjects, this archive of Time is fully searchable from its first issue in March 1923 to December 2000. It’s a great place for readers and researchers to find out more about how our recent past thought of itself.
